high_descs: Go across the room to the green garbage bin, on the floor, just past the counter to your right.
Pull out the apple inside the green garbage bin.
Turn back towards the door at the end of the kitchen and go towards it until you reach the refrigerator on your right.
Place the apple on the second shelf, inside the refrigerator, wait a moment for it to chill, then remove the apple from the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and go across the kitchen to the sink on your right.
Place the apple in the front, left corner of the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in the sink.

high_descs: Move forward and turn right, then face the trash can on the right.
Pick up the apple from the trash can.
Carry the apple and turn to the right, then right again and find the fridge on the left side.
Open the fridge and place the apple inside. Shut the fridge and open it again. Take out the apple and shut the door.
Take the apple and turn to the left and face the sink on the right.
Place the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple and place it in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the green waste basket to your right behind the counter.
Pick up the apple inside the waste basket.
Turn around and walk to the fridge to your right.
Open the fridge, place the apple on the rack, close the fridge door to chill the apple, and remove the apple from the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the sink to your right.
Place the chilled apple inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple in the sink.
